Column Description: Case count in a particular zip code
Total population in the given zip code as of 2010
percentage of COVID cases to total population in a given zip code.
A Record may be suppressed if the population of a zip code is less than or equal to 1500 or the number of cases is less than 5.
Zip code aggregates may not match available county aggregates because zip codes may overlap counties, and because of the above mentioned lower count data suppression.
